div.chi-grid
  .chi-col.-w--12
    .chi-breadcrumb
      ol.-text--normal
        li.chi-breadcrumb__item
          a(href="https://www.w3.org/TR/WCAG20" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank") WCAG 2.0 Guideline
        li.chi-breadcrumb__item
          a(href="https://www.w3.org/TR/WCAG20/#visual-audio-contrast" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank") 1.4 Distinguishable
        li.chi-breadcrumb__item
          a(href="https://www.w3.org/TR/WCAG20/#visual-audio-contrast-text-presentation" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank") 1.4.5 Images of Text
  .chi-col.-w--12
    .-lh--3
      .chi-badge.-dark.-outline.-xs(data-tooltip="Content must be presentable to users in ways they can perceive." data-position="bottom")
        span Perceivable
      .chi-badge.-dark.-outline.-xs.-ml--1(data-tooltip="Requirements must be satisfied to pass WCAG 2.0 Level AA Success Criteria." data-position="bottom")
        span Level AA
  .chi-col.-w--12
    p.-text
      | <strong>Benefits:</strong> Blind disabilities.
    p.-text
      | Text is used to convey information rather than images of text. Achieve desired default visual presentation, to enable people who require a particular visual presentation 
      | of text to be able to adjust the text presentation as needed.
  .chi-col.-w--12
    .chi-card.-s--1.-rounded.-mb--3.-mt--1
      .chi-card__header
        .chi-card__title
          | How to pass
      .chi-card__content.-px--3
        ul.accessibility-checklist
          li 
            | Are images used to present text?
          li 
            | Is text embedded in images?
          li 
            | Is actual text used instead images of text?

